articles.title: Killing cancer takes guts: lessons learned from the manipulation of gut microbiome and immunotherapy for the future of urothelial carcinoma.
articles.summary:
Here's a clear, concise summary sentence:

Manipulating gut bacteria composition may improve immunotherapy effectiveness for patients with urothelial carcinoma by enhancing immune system response.

articles.title: Test: Breakthrough in Lung Cancer Treatment
articles.summary: A new targeted therapy successfully treated 60% of advanced lung cancer patients with specific genetic mutations, offering hope for improved outcomes.
